              "chord": "",
              "text": "He chose me for the purpose He planned,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To express Him, that’s why He made man,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And to represent God as a king,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "One day ruling with Him o’er all things."
            }
